            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-226] exists calls fails on server if node has null data</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-226</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An NPE will be generated on the server (and resulting in client getting MarshallingException) if exists() is called on a node with null data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;workaround is to create the node with non-null data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;be sure to update the tests for this case&lt;/p&gt;</description>
